      <trans-unit id="widgets.t3information.text" approved="yes">
        <source><![CDATA[TYPO3 CMS is an enterprise-class, Open Source Content Management System, used internationally to build and manage websites of all types, from small sites for non-profits to multilingual enterprise solutions for large corporations.<br /><br />For further information visit <a href="https://typo3.org/typo3-cms/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">typo3.org</a>.<br /><br />TYPO3 CMS is <b>freely available</b> under the <a href="https://typo3.org/project/licenses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">TYPO3-license (GNU/GPL)</a>.<br /><br />You are using version %s - Copyright %s %s]]></source>
        <target state="final"><![CDATA[TYPO3 CMS est un système de gestion de contenu Open Source, utilisé internationalement pour construire et gérer des sites web de tous types, des petits sites à but non lucratif aux solutions multilingues complexes pour les grandes entreprises.<br /><br />Pour plus d'informations visitez <a href="https://typo3.org/typo3-cms/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">typo3.org</a>.<br /><br />Le CMS TYPO3 est <b>librement disponible</b> sous la <a href="https://typo3.org/project/licenses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">licence TYPO3 (GNU/GPL)</a>.<br /><br />Vous utilisez la version %s - Copyright %s %s]]></target>
      </trans-unit>
